he hardening instructions regarding `bootstrap_identity` were already addressed in the existing daemon startup flow (`my-claw/tools/cypherclaw_daemon.py` and `my-claw/tools/daemon.py`), and no further changes were needed there.\n","file_path":"sdp/verification/t-056d-verify.md"}}
